  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-05 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A VerificationActivity for Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is declared via hasVerificationActivity but no Evidence in the package references that activity via prov:wasGeneratedBy, creating an activity-evidence consistency gap (W-CON-05).",
