      "rationale": "NIH is the primary validation QoI and matches the COU decision QoI. However, sub-lethal hemolysis markers (free plasma hemoglobin, lactate dehydrogenase) not validated separately. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
