      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on geometry and operating conditions representative of COU device. FDA generic pump geometry is an acceptable surrogate only if geometric similarity metrics documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry differs from proprietary VAD geometry in impeller blade count and volute design. Geometric similarity ratio not formally documented. Validation activities provide indirect but not direct evidence for COU device. Achieved level 2."
